src:
Stockholmsbörsen stängde på rött – Ratos mot strömmen
Efter måndagens rekordnoteringar backade Stockholmsbörsen under tisdagens handel. Både OMXSPI och OMXS30 backade 0,1 procent. Investmentbolaget Ratos rusade 12,6 procent efter succérapporten. 
05 Nov 2019, 16:30 by Victor Hultgren, Nyhetsbyrån Direkt

text:
The Stockholm Stock Exchange closed on red - Ratos against the current
Following Monday's record prices, the Stockholm Stock Exchange reversed during Tuesday's trading. Both OMXSPI and OMXS30 backed 0.1 percent. Investment company Ratos rushed 12.6 percent after the success report.
05 Nov 2019, 16:30 by Victor Hultgren, News Agency Direct
